des:
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your smart devices - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap, or Echo Show.
Connect Alexa to your Girafit products in a few simple steps:
1. Download our “Girafit” app in the Android or iOS app market;
2. Register one Girafit account in our "Girafit" app;
3. You need to have some Girafit devices in hand;
4. Configure these devices in our “Girafit” app and assign appropriate names to your devices, which will be used in "Girafit" skills;
5. Download the Amazon "Alexa" app from the Android, iOS, or Amazon app market;
6. Configure Echo with the "Alexa" app;
7. Search for the "Girafit" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
8. Click to enable the skill for "Girafit", and you'll be navigated to the Girafit login page;
9. Input your Girafit account username and password, and you'll be redirected to the success page;
10. Now all setup is finished.

You can enjoy voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, Show Camera"
“Alexa, Hide the Camera"
“Alexa, Stop the Camera”
